{"tid":1390270,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"颱風過後 希望各區有心人修復連儂牆","createTime":"2019-07-31T06:05:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-01T03:22:59.000Z","uid":134924,"like":23,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"8f1b941b60947609ccbe73aa08caa3ba5c4b16bf","tid":1390270,"uid":134924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T06:05:16.000Z","msg":"連儂牆係一個運動嘅精神體現<br />\n同時係一個重要嘅文宣平台<br />\n<br />\n唔好做三分鐘熱度嘅香港人 <br />\n如果連儂牆變得溶溶爛爛 不修邊幅<br />\n其實 某程度 都反映緊我地對<br />\n我地所爭取 所追求嘅野 變得模糊<br />\n希望各位三思 <br />\n<br />\n加強未來文宣 香港場仗未打完嫁<br />\n<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n保持熱度 抗爭到底"},{"pid":"7a02d1ce4e4eceb61c1408cb7387d85f78866baf","tid":1390270,"uid":134924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T06:07:15.000Z","msg":"8.5 全港罷工"},{"pid":"06c028b37e621066a62dd03bea7df9e4d1e58a97","tid":1390270,"uid":134924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T06:10:43.000Z","msg":"8.3 重遊旺角"},{"pid":"138ffa4cb5204c5bc1e64855eee0553a052bc9d2","tid":1390270,"uid":134924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T06:15:34.000Z","msg":"8.4 將軍澳遊行"},{"pid":"3532ce7f4c3a5de09e6749098519a38a21d01be9","tid":1390270,"uid":275074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T06:30:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1502897435e23d346f6b76092b04f885845c349c","tid":1390270,"uid":134924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T06:36:50.000Z","msg":"8.4 同日港島游行"},{"pid":"4387a4ec68908d6ffa3626e53fbf3dbc109aa9c1","tid":1390270,"uid":134924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T06:47:51.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"16c975e74cb0fcaddbc6e11055292c90a9f3820c","tid":1390270,"uid":226955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T06:48:32.000Z","msg":"不要說「推」，試着説「8月5號齊罷工」<br />\n<br />\n範例：<br />\n<blockquote>#我係香港人 <br />\n#我會參與8月5日三罷 <br />\n#罷工罷市罷課</blockquote>"},{"pid":"19b8ef37d8a15b203a3ae209730ad4412af45b87","tid":1390270,"